statements: SELECT * FROM VoterTurnout WHERE age > 18;
SELECT voter_name, age, vote_status FROM VoterTurnout WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT voter_name, gender, precinct_id FROM VoterTurnout ORDER BY voter_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM VoterTurnout WHERE vote_status = 'Voted' AND age > 18 ORDER BY age ASC;
SELECT voter_name, gender, precinct_id FROM VoterTurnout WHERE gender = 'Female' ORDER BY precinct_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM VoterTurnout WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY voter_name DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT voter_name, age, gender FROM VoterTurnout WHERE gender = 'Male' AND vote_status = 'Voted' ORDER BY age ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_voters FROM VoterTurnout WHERE vote_status = 'Voted';
SELECT voter_name, age, precinct_id FROM VoterTurnout WHERE age < 25 AND precinct_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT DISTINCT gender FROM VoterTurnout WHERE age BETWEEN 40 AND 50 ORDER BY gender DESC;
SELECT * FROM voter_turnout;
SELECT name, age, gender FROM voter_turnout WHERE age > 18;
SELECT voter_id, name, income_level FROM voter_turnout t JOIN demographics d ON t.voter_id = d.voter_id;
SELECT * FROM demographics WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT voter_id, ethnicity, vote_status FROM voter_turnout WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT * FROM voter_turnout WHERE age > 30 AND gender = 'Male';
SELECT name, age, vote_status FROM voter_turnout WHERE gender = 'Female' ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT voter_id, location, income_level FROM demographics WHERE education_level = 'Bachelor' ORDER BY income_level ASC;
SELECT name, age, gender, vote_status FROM voter_turnout WHERE gender = 'Male' AND age BETWEEN 18 AND 25;
SELECT * FROM demographics WHERE location LIKE '%City%' AND income_level IN ('High', 'Medium') ORDER BY voter_id;
SELECT * FROM voter_turnout;
SELECT name, age FROM voter_turnout ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT name, gender FROM voter_turnout JOIN voter_demographics ON voter_turnout.voter_id = voter_demographics.voter_id;
SELECT voter_id, ethnicity FROM voter_demographics WHERE occupation = 'Teacher';
SELECT AVG(age) AS avg_age FROM voter_turnout;
SELECT * FROM voter_turnout;
SELECT name, age, registration_date FROM voter_turnout ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT v.name, v.age, va.turnout_status FROM voter_turnout v JOIN voter_analysis va ON v.voter_id = va.voter_id WHERE va.turnout_status='High';
SELECT vd.gender, vd.ethnicity, va.analysis_date FROM voter_demographics vd JOIN voter_analysis va ON vd.voter_id = va.voter_id WHERE va.analysis_date > '2021-01-01';

SELECT v.name, vd.ethnicity, va.turnout_status FROM voter_turnout v JOIN voter_demographics vd ON v.voter_id = vd.voter_id JOIN voter_analysis va ON v.voter_id = va.voter_id WHERE v.age > 30 AND vd.occupation='Educator';
SELECT voter_name, age, gender FROM voter_demographics WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT election_name, election_date FROM voting_history WHERE vote_status='Voted' ORDER BY election_date ASC;
SELECT candidate_name, party_affiliation FROM election_candidates WHERE party_affiliation='Independent' ORDER BY candidate_name ASC;
SELECT district_name, total_voters, voting_location FROM election_districts WHERE total_voters < 5000 ORDER BY district_name ASC;
SELECT voter_name, age, location FROM voter_demographics WHERE age BETWEEN 25 AND 40 ORDER BY voter_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM voter_demographics WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY voter_name DESC;
SELECT voter_name, gender FROM voter_demographics WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT v.voter_name, vh.election_name, vh.election_date FROM voter_demographics v JOIN voting_history vh ON v.voter_id = vh.voter_id WHERE vh.vote_status = 'Voted' ORDER BY vh.election_date DESC;

SELECT ed.district_name, ec.candidate_name, ec.party_affiliation FROM election_districts ed JOIN election_candidates ec ON ed.district_id = ec.election_district_id WHERE ed.total_voters > 1000 ORDER BY ec.candidate_name ASC;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(voter_id)) AS total_voters, AVG(age) AS avg_age FROM voter_demographics;
SELECT * FROM VoterDemographics;
SELECT name, age, gender FROM VoterDemographics;
SELECT address FROM VoterDemographics WHERE voter_id = 123;
SELECT voter_id, election_date, voted FROM VoterTurnout WHERE precinct_id = 456;
SELECT election_date, total_votes, winner_name FROM ElectionResults;
SELECT name, age, gender FROM VoterDemographics WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT * FROM VoterDemographics INNER JOIN VoterTurnout ON VoterDemographics.voter_id = VoterTurnout.voter_id;
SELECT DISTINCT city, state FROM PrecinctInfo WHERE state = 'CA';
SELECT precinct_name, total_votes, winner_name FROM PrecinctInfo INNER JOIN ElectionResults ON PrecinctInfo.precinct_id = ElectionResults.election_id;
SELECT analysis_id, age_group, analysis_date FROM DemographicAnalysis WHERE voter_turnout = TRUE ORDER BY analysis_date DESC;
